title: Sesame greens and bean sprouts
ingredients: ['30 g (1 oz) sesame seeds', '2 tbsp sunflower oil', '1 onion, chopped', '2 garlic cloves, chopped', '1 small Savoy cabbage, about 300 g (10½ oz), finely shredded', '½ head of Chinese leaves, finely shredded', '170 g (6 oz) bean sprouts', '4 tbsp oyster sauce', 'salt and pepper']
